<p>
<lb n="1"/>cuntarapāṇṭiya<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu 5vatu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>tiruvāppaṉūr Ūrāy Icainta Ūrom cakkarapāṇipūvaṉāṉa teṉṉavaṉ Iṭaikkuḷa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>�ṉum kiḻavaṉāṇmālaiyāṉa kulaicekarac ceṅkumuṭirāyaṉum Uyyavantāṉ mātaṉāṉa virapāṇṭiya muttaraiyaṉum Uḷḷiṭṭo <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>yaṉum mātaṉ comaṉum Uḷḷiṭṭomum nammāl tevaṉ tecappukaḷnallūr vaḷaiyiṟcuṟṟum Iṟaiyili muṟcūṭṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>m Aṟakkoṇṭu Ivvempalil puṉcetiruk <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nāyaṉār tiruvana<hi rend="grantha">ndīśvara</hi>nāyaṉār koyilil Ā<hi rend="grantha">dicaṇḍheśvara</hi>piḷḷaiyāṟku nica <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>ṇipūvaṉāṉa teṉṉavaṉ Iṭaikkuḷanāṭṭaraiyaṉ Eḻuttu cetiyarāyaṉ Eḻuttu Ippaṭi<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied> kivai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> tevanāṉateṉṉavaṉ peraiyaṉ taṟkuriyānataṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>tu poruḷaṟak koṇṭa Uyyavantāṉ muttaṉāṉa perumāḷ koṉappaṉ taṟkuṟiyātanmaikku <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> konappaṉ taṟkuṟiyātaṉmaikku muttu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

